welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Mitchellville! This charming city is known for its beautiful parks, friendly community, and delicious local food. We invite you to explore and experience all that Mitchellville has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tipton AAF Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport handles all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: Terminal A primarily serves American Airlines and its codeshare partners.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: Terminal B is used by Delta Air Lines and its partners, as well as some international carriers.

terminals.name: Terminal C
terminals.description: Terminal C is home to United Airlines and its alliance partners.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport serves as the hub for most airlines and offers a variety of shops, restaurants, and amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport primarily serves Southwest Airlines and offers a variety of shops, restaurants, and amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport serves a variety of airlines and offers a variety of shops, restaurants, and amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C at Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport serves a variety of airlines and offers a variety of shops, restaurants, and amenities for travelers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Montgomery County Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Montgomery County Airport is exclusively for private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network throughout the terminal.
